if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B1EBXtIF1SU/?igshid=9xejtb5cdkbp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1EBXtIF1SU%2F%3Figshid%3D9xejtb5cdkbp&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=f1f9141a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1EBXtIF1SU%2F%3Figshid%3D9xejtb5cdkbp&h=12e5a3fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B1EBXtIF1SU/?igshid=9xejtb5cdkbp</a><br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n此post已得事主同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事源係事主去個大陸rapper到講岀佢地要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">翻牆哩個事實既真相</span>，之後佢地個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玻璃心</span>碎到一地都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n真心好奇一問，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">九龍城，八仙嶺同七龍珠</span></strong>係咩門派？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有冇人可以話我知佢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">詳細地址？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瀋陽咁大，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要有佢準確嘅地址先至可以去應約</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最後，818大遊行，約定你</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uMySiR3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMySiR3.png&h=9ee582af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16ddfecf86d9e028bbfac80a728a2dc6f81b9994","tid":1472914,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已